1886 // This is a terrible hack to workaround the fact that VRControllerState_t and VREvent_t were
1887 // originally mis-compiled with the wrong packing for Linux and OSX.
1888  [UnmanagedFunctionPointer(CallingConvention.StdCall)]
1889  internal delegate bool _PollNextEventPacked(ref VREvent_t_Packed pEvent,uint uncbVREvent);
1890  [StructLayout(LayoutKind.Explicit)]
1891  struct PollNextEventUnion
1892  {
1893  [FieldOffset(0)]
1894  public IVRSystem._PollNextEvent pPollNextEvent;
1895  [FieldOffset(0)]
1896  public _PollNextEventPacked pPollNextEventPacked;
1897  }
1898  public bool PollNextEvent(ref VREvent_t pEvent,uint uncbVREvent)
1899  {
1900 #if !UNITY_METRO
1901  if ((System.Environment.OSVersion.Platform == System.PlatformID.MacOSX) ||

2937 // This is a terrible hack to workaround the fact that VRControllerState_t and VREvent_t were
2938 // originally mis-compiled with the wrong packing for Linux and OSX.
2939  [UnmanagedFunctionPointer(CallingConvention.StdCall)]

3246  (System.Environment.OSVersion.Platform == System.PlatformID.Unix))
3247  {

3251  u.pGetComponentState = FnTable.GetComponentState;
3252  bool packed_result = u.pGetComponentStatePacked(pchRenderModelName,pchComponentName,ref state_packed,ref pState,ref pComponentState);
3253 
3254  state_packed.Unpack(ref pControllerState);

6283  public static CVRSystem Init(ref EVRInitError peError, EVRApplicationType eApplicationType = EVRApplicationType.VRApplication_Scene, string pchStartupInfo= "")
6284  {
6285  try
6286  {
6287  VRToken = InitInternal2(ref peError, eApplicationType, pchStartupInfo);
6288  }
6289  catch (EntryPointNotFoundException)
6290  {
6291  VRToken = InitInternal(ref peError, eApplicationType);
6292  }
6293 
6294  OpenVRInternal_ModuleContext.Clear();
6295 
6296  if (peError != EVRInitError.None)
6297  return null;
6298 
6299  bool bInterfaceValid = IsInterfaceVersionValid(IVRSystem_Version);
6300  if (!bInterfaceValid)
6301  {
6302  ShutdownInternal();
6303  peError = EVRInitError.Init_InterfaceNotFound;
6304  return null;
6305  }
6306 
6307  return OpenVR.System;
6308  }
